## Laravel Module Maker — AI Instructions (generated by `jw:ai:init` v{{ packageVersion }})

This project uses a modular architecture managed by jackwander/laravel-module-maker.

- Read `.ai/summary.md` before generating code; complete guidelines live in the `.ai/` directory (`ai-rules.md`, `conventions.md`, `generators.md`, `architecture.md`, `workflow.md`).
- Scaffold module files ONLY through the `jw:*` artisan generators — never create module boilerplate by hand.
- Features live in isolated modules; keep business logic in module Services, validation in FormRequests, API output in Resources.
- {{ mcpNote }}

Regenerate with `php artisan jw:ai:init --refresh`.
